    <link href="http://pauleveritt.github.io/posts/type_hinting/" />
    <author>
      <name>Paul Everitt</name>
    </author>
    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Python 3.5 introduces &lt;em&gt;type hinting&lt;/em&gt; to help code-writing during
development. Let&amp;#8217;s take a look at this feature and show it in action.&lt;/p&gt;
</content>
